FBIS3-23042 "jptot008__l94004" JPRS-TOT-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 1 March 1994 INTERNATIONAL Delhi Reports French Offer To Help Fight Terrorism BK1202114994 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0245 GMT 12 Feb 94 BK1202114994 Delhi All India Radio Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] France has offered to cooperate with India in the fight against terrorism. The external affairs minister, Mr. Dinesh Singh, who met the French interior minister, Mr. Charles Pasqua, in Paris yesterday outlined the problems faced by India due to terrorism. According to the Indian Embassay in Paris, Mr. Pasqua expressed full understanding and stated that France is prepared to cooperate with India in combatting terrorism.
